results.name: Triangle T(n,d) (listed row-wise: T(1,1)=1, T(2,1)=1, T(2,2)=1, T(3,1)=2, T(3,2)=0, T(3,3)=1, ...) giving the number of n-edge general plane trees with root degree d that are fixed by Catalan Automorphisms A057511/A057512 (Deep rotation of general parenthesizations/plane trees).
link: Index entries for sequences related to parenthesizing
xref: The row sums equal to the left edge shifted left once = A057546 = first row of A079216 (the latter gives the Maple procedure PFixedByA057511). Cf. also A079218, A079219, A079220, A079221, A079222 and A003056 and A002262.
